
ABOUT

An experimental tabbed button window decoration for Xfce window manager (xfwm4) .
Inspired from Alfheim Online user interface.
(Kirito's harem watching BOB3 scene).

INSTALLING

- Extract "ArchedgeUI" and "ArchedgeUI 32px" folder to /home/youruser/.themes
- Open Window Manager settings (xfwm4-settings)
- Select theme and make sure button layout is : title shade hide maximize close
